            ^"Skills" LIST OF STRING ["Cthulhu Mythos 70%", "History (Earth) 75%", "History (Shambhala) 90%", "Lore (Buddhism) 90%", "Occult 90%", "Psychology 75%", "Spot Hidden 80%", "any (as appropriate) 100%", "Spells: Curse*, Melt Flesh, Sword Siddhi*, Wrack, plus any other spells of the Keeper's choosing"]
            ^"Sanity Loss" STRING "0/1D4 Sanity points to see a Lord in humanoid form, 1/1D6 Sanity points to see a Lord in sengye form"
            ^"Description" STRING "Statistics shown are sample 1 (leader) of three. Their outward appearances are merely an illusion formed by the investigators' minds. In humanoid form they attack with razor-sharp fingernails or a phurba. In Sengye (Snow Lion) form they use Roar of Silence and either bite or claw."
